session_history.content: What is the purpose of the `resusagespsV` view?

The resusagespsV view provides information about resource usage statistics, specifically pertaining to stored procedures.

Key Observations

  • The provided list of tables indicates that resusagespsV is one of many views related to performance monitoring, resource tracking, and database statistics within the system.
  • Other views with similar naming conventions (e.g., ResScpuView, ResIvprView, ResUsageSawt) suggest that a suite of views collectively monitor various resource consumption aspects.
